titles.title: Recognizing Rett Reef off the coast of San Leon, Texas, in Galveston Bay, and all those associated with bringing the project to fruition.
Recognizing Rett Reef off the coast of San Leon, Texas, in Galveston Bay, and all those associated with bringing the project to fruition.

action.text: Referred to the House Committee on Natural Resources.

bill.summary: This resolution recognizes (1) the contribution of Rett Reef in Galveston Bay, off the coast of San Leon, Texas, for its value to the Texas Gulf Coast; and (2) those associated with bringing the Rett Reef project to fruition.
